import React from 'react'
import { Input, Grid } from "@nextui-org/react";
const Signup = () => {
  return (
    <Grid.Container gap={4}>
    <Grid>
      <Input 
        underlined 
        labelPlaceholder="Default" 
        color="default" />
    </Grid>
    <Grid>
      <Input 
        underlined 
        labelPlaceholder="Primary" 
        color="primary" 
      />
    </Grid>
    <Grid>
      <Input 
        underlined 
        labelPlaceholder="Secondary" 
        color="secondary" 
      />
    </Grid>
    <Grid>
      <Input 
        underlined 
        labelPlaceholder="Success" 
        color="success" 
      />
    </Grid>
    <Grid>
      <Input 
        underlined 
        labelPlaceholder="Warning" 
        color="warning" 
      />
    </Grid>
    <Grid>
      <Input 
        underlined 
        labelPlaceholder="Error" 
        color="error" 
      />
    </Grid>
  </Grid.Container>
  )
}

export default Signup
